Based on the repository summary and focusing on connectivity, here's a PlantUML component diagram for the ebu_PlugIt system:

```plantuml
@startuml ebu_PlugIt

package "PlugIt Server" {
  [PlugIt API] as API
  [PlugIt Core] as Core
  [Project Specific Logic] as ProjectLogic
  [Database] as DB
}

[Client Application] as Client

Client -right-> API : HTTP/HTTPS
API -down-> Core : Internal calls
Core -right-> ProjectLogic : Executes
ProjectLogic -down-> DB : CRUD Operations

@enduml
```